anded pitcher)|Rodr\u00edguez]]''' (13\u20135) || [[Luis Cessa|Cessa]] (1\u20134) ||\u2014|| '''[[Fenway Park]]''' || 36,201 || 108\u201354 || [https://gd2.mlb.com/content/game/mlb/year_2018/month_09/day_30/gid_2018_09_30_nyamlb_bosmlb_1/boxscore_col.html W1]\n|}\n</div></div>\n'''Reference''':<ref name=\"schedule\">{{cite web|url=http://espn.go.com/mlb/team/schedule/_/name/bos/year/2018/boston-red-sox|title=Boston Red Sox 2018 Schedule \u2013 Red Sox Home and Away - ESPN|website=ESPN|accessdate=October 23, 2017}}</ref>\n|}\n\n===Postseason game log===\n{| class=\"toccolours collapsible\" style=\"width:100%; clear:both; margin:1.5em auto; text-align:center\"\n|-\n! colspan=2 style=\"background:#c60c30; border: 3px solid #024; color:#fff\" | <span style=\"color:#fff; font-family:calibri, serif\"><big><center>Boston Red Sox 2018 Postseason Game Log (11\u20133)</center></big></span>\n|- valign=\"top\"\n|<div class=\"NavFrame collapsed\">\n<div class=\"NavHead\" style=\"background:#024; border: 4px solid #c60c30; color:#fff\"><span style=\"color:#fff; font-family:calibri, serif\"><big>[[2018 American League Division Series|<span style=\"color:white;\">American League Division Series</span>]] vs. [[2018 New York Yankees season|<span style=\"color:white;\">New York Yankees</span>]] (3\u20131)</big></span></div>\n<div class=\"NavContent\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! style=\"width:4%;\"| #/\n! style=\"width:11%;\"| Date\n! style=\"width:11%;\"| Opponent\n! style=\"width:8%;\"| Score\n! style=\"width:14%;\"| Win\n! style=\"width:14%;\"| Loss\n! style=\"width:14%;\"| Save\n! style=\"width:14%;\"| Stadium\n! style=\"width:8%;\"| Attendance\n! style=\"width:5%;\"| Series\n! style=\"width:5%;\"| Box/<br />Streak\n|- style=\"text-align:center; background:#bfb;\"\n| 1 || October 5 || [[2018 New York Yankees season|Yankees]] || 5\u20134 || '''[[Chris Sale|Sale]]''' (1\u20130) || [[J. A. Happ|Happ]] (0\u20131) || '''[[Craig Kimbrel|Kimbrel]]''' (1) |